00:30:08,590 --> 00:30:17,870
In that racing we forget about the way we
eat our food, then we rush about.

328
00:30:17,870 --> 00:30:28,010
We don’t even give rest to our different
organs as it is required to balance its activities,

329
00:30:28,010 --> 00:30:40,590
[so] what happens that a thing like spleen
get so upset, it’s so upset, that it does

330
00:30:40,590 --> 00:30:43,690
not know when to create more blood cells and
when not to create.

