00:32:43,630 --> 00:32:45,990
He’s a horrible fellow.

354
00:32:45,990 --> 00:32:53,730
He has never sought anything good.

355
00:32:53,730 --> 00:32:54,890
He has no compassion.

356
00:32:54,890 --> 00:32:57,460
He has no love.

357
00:32:57,460 --> 00:33:00,360
He’s for himself, a very selfish and a tyrannical
person.

358
00:33:00,360 --> 00:33:05,450
Tomorrow if Hitler comes and say, “Mother,
you give me Realisation."

359
00:33:05,450 --> 00:33:10,850
Do you think Divine is supposed to give him
Realisation, because he thinks no end of himself?

