00:33:17,850 --> 00:33:22,169
It is not for you to decide for the Divine.

362
00:33:22,169 --> 00:33:25,309
The Divine has to say that you are all right.

363
00:33:25,309 --> 00:33:28,730
It’s just the other way round.

364
00:33:28,730 --> 00:33:31,200
Because you may do whatever you like.

